Privacy Policy

Last updated: 08.28.2024

Liber Creative LLC (“us”, “we”, or “our”) operates the PI Creation Tool computer application and subsidiary applications and add-ons (the “Service”).

This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of personal data when you use our Service and the choices you have associated with that data.

Information Collection and Use

We collect several different types of information after moderation for various purposes to provide safety of our Service to you.

Data collection

Personal Data: We don't collect users' data, because we are creating tools - not data collectors, we use moderation to identify users, who use additional features, that may cause illegal use.
Usage Data: User data can be collected after moderation process and can be used only if there was an attempt of illegal use.

Use of Data

Liber Creative LLC uses the collected data for:

To provide socail security services with information about illegal use of our Service.

The security of your data is important to us, but remember that no method of transmission over the Internet or method of electronic storage is 100% secure. While we strive to use commercially acceptable means to protect your Personal Data, we cannot guarantee its absolute security.
So think twice, if you really need the features, that require moderation.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

